### Admin Workflow:
    When releaseing a new version do the below
        Increase version in pubspec.yaml:YAML   version: 1.0.1+3     # ← Increase this
        Build new version
            flutter clean
            flutter pub get
            flutter build web --release
            firebase deploy --only hosting
            flutter build apk --target-platform android-arm64 --release
        Upload APK to Firebase App Distribution.
        Copy the new download URL from App Distribution.
        Update Remote Config:
            Go to Remote Config - https://console.firebase.google.com/project/ctp-job-cards/config/env/firebase
                Click on each parameter and update:
                latest_version → 1.0.1
                latest_build → 3
                download_url → (paste new URL)
                release_notes → "Fixed bugs + improved performance"
                force_update → false (or true if critical)
    Click Publish changes



